        "column_BgX46J": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Emily ChenEmily Chen",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/lady_1_prod.webp",
            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "5h ago",
            "post_text": "<p>Finally, my bathroom counter doesn't look like a mess during vacations! I love how aesthetic and clean this looks. I put my cleanser, toner, moisturizer, and body wash all in one place. No more fumbling with 4 different tiny caps in a cramped hotel shower. 10/10 recommendation!</p><p>♥♥♥♥♥♥</p>",
