    "collapsible_content_nJrYmE": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_content_6w9ntk": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is it TSA approved for carry-on luggage?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! Each internal bottle has a capacity of 30ml (1.0 oz), which is well within the TSA limit of 100ml per container for carry-on bags. You can breeze through airport security without any issues.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_njkpDd": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Can I use it for thick lotions or oils?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>It works best with standard liquid toiletries like shampoo, conditioner, body wash, and face serums. We do not recommend using it for extremely thick pastes or pure oils to ensure a smooth dispensing experience.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_CVU4Bm": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is the bottle truly leak-proof?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely. The dispenser features a secure pump-lock mechanism and a sturdy outer shell to prevent any accidental presses or leaks, keeping your clothes and luggage safe and dry.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_ETX7yr": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "How do I refill the bottles?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Simply twist the top cover counter-clockwise to open. Pull out the 4 internal bottles, fill them with your favorite products, and snap them back into their slots. It takes less than a minute!</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_HTVjPX": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is it easy to clean?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. The internal bottles are removable and can be rinsed with warm soapy water. We recommend cleaning them between refills if you decide to change the type of liquid inside.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_Ahw39W": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What materials is it made of?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Our travel dispenser is made from high-quality, BPA-free ABS and PET materials. It is durable, impact-resistant, and safe for all your skincare products.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_z4rFdy": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What if I’m not happy with the product?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>We offer a 90-day risk-free trial. If you’re not completely satisfied with your purchase, just contact our support team for a full refund or exchange.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
      },
